<ac:structured-macro ac:name="note">
  <ac:parameter ac:name="title">Phase 2.5 — Release Readiness Check (Standalone Jenkins Feedback Pipeline — No Deployment)</ac:parameter>
  <ac:rich-text-body>
    <p>This is a <strong>separate Jenkins job</strong> triggered manually by the release manager before NFT or Production deployments. It validates release readiness by running all quality gates against the release branch <strong>without deploying anything</strong>. Build is marked <strong>UNSTABLE</strong> (not failed) if any control fails — giving visibility without blocking.</p>
    <p><strong>Parameters:</strong> <code>TARGET_ORG</code> (NFT or Prod) · <code>releaseVersion</code> (e.g. 263.0) · <code>delta</code> (true/false) · run flags below</p>
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th><strong>Control</strong></th>
          <th><strong>Flag</strong></th>
          <th><strong>Checks</strong></th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Unit Testing</strong></td>
          <td><code>runUnitTest</code></td>
          <td>Apex code coverage ≥ 75% · Apex unit test pass rate = 100% · Jest overall coverage ≥ 35% · Jest Dynamo components ≥ 70%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Security</strong></td>
          <td><code>runSSAPScan</code></td>
          <td>SSAP vulnerability scan</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Functional Testing</strong></td>
          <td><code>runAutomatedFunctionalTests</code></td>
          <td>Playwright regression / smoke tests ≥ 80% pass rate</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Traceability</strong></td>
          <td><code>runTestTraceability</code></td>
          <td>All requirements mapped to tests · All mapped tests executed and passed (100%) · No open High/Critical priority bugs · No open Low/Medium priority bugs · No defects in Triage · No production defects outside SLA · Manual regression test pass rate = 100%</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p><strong>Outcome:</strong>
      <ac:structured-macro ac:name="status"><ac:parameter ac:name="colour">Yellow</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name="title">UNSTABLE if any control fails</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro>
      — Sends detailed PASS/FAIL email per control to the release manager.</p>
  </ac:rich-text-body>
</ac:structured-macro>

